Before Michele collected her prize, the whole "Glee" cast accepted the Choice TV Comedy award, also paying tribute to Monteith. After Michele's emotional acceptance speech, a picture of Monteith was displayed on the screen with the text "Cory Monteith: 1982-2013."

"Glee" returns to Fox on Thursday, Sept. 26, and the third episode of season 5 will address Monteith's untimely death.

